==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forgiving
<hw>For*giv"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Disposed to forgive; inclined
to overlook offenses; mild; merciful; compassionate; placable; <as>as, a
<ex>forgiving</ex> temper</as>.</def></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>For*giv"ing*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>For*giv"ing*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms> <rj><au>J. C.
Shairp.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>forgivingness</ent>⟦br⟧
